{"tid":2083472,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日分咗手⋯⋯啦","createTime":"2020-06-28T18:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T03:34:16.000Z","uid":314203,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2be8496764e07ac66eed8fe7555efb2dd1b1af77","tid":2083472,"uid":314203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:31:51.000Z","msg":"說在我口，痛在我心。啱啱講咗分手了。其實前個排，已經感覺到我地唔同咗，唔係再好似以前咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲記得..當初我地識個陣...一切都好美好。我冇諗過個次係我地最後一次見，最後一次嘅擁抱，最後一次你鍚我。算啦我已經喊到打唔到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想再諗當初了。其實唔好覺得講分手個個永遠都係衰人，可能佢先係最傷個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你明唔明。好痛好痛好痛。我唔想呢個係最好嘅選擇⋯⋯點解你仲可以咁平靜回答我⋯⋯⋯⋯原來我地由個刻開始已經完咗再冇關係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來呢個係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab35ee1376d727454c6e291af4c492b968120b1b","tid":2083472,"uid":215293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:33:35.000Z","msg":"好好抖下 日子會過"},{"pid":"048744b2499bd2675237fdc464aed18419c48dd8","tid":2083472,"uid":191453,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e9opumH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe9opumH.jpg&h=3efce2a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9625e1abd745776c11a32f89379ea8b42e68ece2","tid":2083472,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:43:38.000Z","msg":"我做著你水泡先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f0bb3f6e1475a851bcbd47a3f55d295e8df5e6","tid":2083472,"uid":318876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:54:49.000Z","msg":"可能佢抑壓住情緒，無表露出嚟啫<br />\n男人